org.nerd4j.csv.registry

Class CSVAbstractRegistry<Entry extends CSVRegistryEntry>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nerd4j.csv.registry.CSVAbstractRegistry<Entry>
  • Type Parameters:
    Entry - type of the entry to build.

    public abstract class CSVAbstractRegistry<Entry extends CSVRegistryEntry>
extends Object
    Abstract implementation of a registry containing the providers able to understand the configured values and provide the related objects.

    Currently the available implementations are:

    • CSVFieldValidatorRegistry
    • CSVFieldConverterRegistry
    • CSVFieldProcessorRegistry
    • CSVToModelBinderFactoryRegistry
    • ModelToCSVBinderFactoryRegistry
    Author:
    Nerd4j Team
